settings.description: World 6-2 from SMB3 2nd Run by Recovery1. The pipe pointers were corrected as it glitched in the original version as well as having the pull-able weeds in place of the beta grass.
Somewhat sunken plains. Apologies for the glitches if any.
Giant enemies among this plains stage.
Munchers and nipper plants are alive and happily active here.
Original level design by Edward Reynolds aka Mari42. Tread carefully.
